{"type": "article", "id": 55854, "title": "一套花器，为世界排名第一的餐厅 Noma 量身而做｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-08-01T23:14:18Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 52311, "name": "Culinesco"}, {"id": 48601, "name": "Regular Company"}, {"id": 52312, "name": "EMKO"}, {"id": 6598, "name": "Noma"}, {"id": 22512, "name": "Good Thing"}, {"id": 25572, "name": "Floris Wubben"}, {"id": 52313, "name": "Frederik Nystrup-Larsen"}, {"id": 52314, "name": "Oliver Sundquist"}, {"id": 52315, "name": "Shinya Yoshida"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 10, "praise_count": 95, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180801204907DOoz0X6QhLysSZAR.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font-kerning: none; color: #999999; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #999999} span.s4 {font-kerning: none; color: #dd4b39; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #dd4b39} span.s5 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s6 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s7 {font-kerning: none; color: #141414; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #141414} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Architectural Silicone Containers by Good Thing</h3><p>在最近的纽约夏季餐馆周期间，布鲁克林设计品牌 Good Thing 推出建筑风格系列的硅胶容器 G3。操刀这个系列的，是东京工业设计师 Shinya Yoshida。</p><p>在设计师之前，他曾是一名汽车修理工。此番新系列的设计，灵感也是取自汽车，强调简单形式满足基本功能。 </p><p>G3 由硅胶制成，可以置于浴室、办公室和厨房等不同风格的空间使用，包括蓝黑色、橄榄绿、薄荷色、铁锈红以及灰白调，也都是时下流行的色彩。它并不局限使用的物品，不管邮票、化妆刷、铅笔还是坚果，都可以盛放。售价 12 美元起，点击这里尝试购买。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180801204949jxsVUH39EXn5pLGh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.612798\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180801204949BduCViERH25YrQfX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.612798\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180801204949TZgCK0WO9Icnurmw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.612798\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180801204949i6VAcavwTzXZHkut.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.612798\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180801204949rJA2DP9X6IRgT1K4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.166304\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180801204949nl4WEItiMhReyJkL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180801204950ZFqbapLtI6rDzueh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.164130\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://supergoodthing.com/collections/home-page\" rel=\"nofollow\">Good Thing</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Mater by Frederik Nystrup-Larsen and Oliver Sundquist for Noma</h3><p>哥本哈根餐厅 Noma，被誉为世界最难订也是最棒的餐厅，曾连续三年被评为全球 50 家最棒餐厅冠军，去年暂停营业后，又于今年 2 月在哥本哈根 Christianshavn 街区重新开放。</p><p>最近，设计师 Frederik Nystrup-Larsen 和 Oliver Sundquist 为 Noma 的新家创造了一系列看起来像是熔岩的旋转式混凝土花瓶 Mater。花瓶的纹理形式是用固体着色水泥雕刻而成。每个单个花瓶都是定制的形状，所以没有两个是相同的。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180801205102YjBrDKJLdUa2tAu3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562793\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180801205104pF5v4mcdDWagtNu7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180801205108uQIM2jypLGYxv7nU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.733503\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201808012051087WMLd2Da8YfjBATF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.760998\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180801205108bcrpD1REwj42GBx6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.283418\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.dezeen.com/2018/08/01/mater-vases-noma-restaurant-copenhagen-frederik-nystrup-larsen-oliver-sundquist/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dezeen</a> 摄影：Simon Knudsen</figcaption></figure></div><h3>Naïve Low Chair by EMKO</h3><p>几年前，丹麦设计工作室 etc.etc. 推出平板包装的座椅 Naïve，最近，他们又为立陶宛家具设计和家居饰品公司 EMKO 设计了 Naïve 的更新版本，较之原版更低矮一些。</p><p>Naïve Low 椅包括八个部件：四个椅腿、两个后杆、一个座椅和一个靠背，它们可以很容易地拧在一起，形成一个舒适的软垫座椅。与原版一样，新版本可以轻松拧开，方便拆卸和移动。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180801205239aLOhxoJG13vblIQ4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180801205239FrbBSaKLqy0pwnEH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180801205240iBsp14qbyr8REFYf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.756250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201808012052406YzuwIOcErVi2hxK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180801205239W2htkN5lo6MTaJfX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180801205240E1Av67WTak2sowH8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.497656\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180801205240mRDSVWoKu0PTH1ya.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.emko-online.lt/\" rel=\"nofollow\">EMKO</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Crystal Twist by Floris Wubben</h3><p>阿姆斯特丹设计师 Floris Wubben 的最新作品，是一款在功能性灯具和艺术品之间找到平衡的吊灯 Crystal Twist。</p><p>它由 HI-MACS 亚克力石制成，HI-MACS 材料通常用于光滑的表面，比如台面，但 Floris Wubben选择使用它来制作灯具。在制作过程中，他发现材料在加热时会被撕裂，便顺着这个结果将其材料裹在灯体模具四周，形成螺旋一般的纹理。当灯点亮时，便给人一种光线透过裂缝迸发出来的感觉。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180801205335ys6iTVENGAgHpqZe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180801205335QfyvW8Z0MVY7Txls.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180801205336clmIUnS8DRu7V9FT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180801205336sPe2JB8IKYDcoSEL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180801205337yeIP7bk0KJBUlGsA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.052344\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180801205337U36oksZj5e8nFQKC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.floriswubben.nl/crystal-twist/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Floris Wubben</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Stone Collection by Regular Company</h3><p>萨格勒布设计工作室 Regular Company 推出最新厨具系列 Stone，将其描述为极简主义、优雅和美观的作品。石头的有机形式定义了这些常规物体的美感。它的形状来自对杵和臼的功能的探索，进而创造出一个极具雕塑感切触觉新奇的产品。</p><p>按照 Regular Company 的说法，Stone 系列试图重新思考人们与物体相互作用的方式。</p><p>大理石托盘的灵感，来自于探索工匠在石材表面上创造各种纹路的传统技术。每一款托盘，都做了不同的表面处理，意在提供不同的触觉对比，使人们能够以创造性的方式使用托盘。例如，在粗糙的质地上研磨香料和草药。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180801205504FdAbKDXtRMTYL1vC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498571\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180801205504IoxyZLPJvdD5YA2f.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180801205505KL1edazP9RhfXouT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180801205505S2d5vPJLOoC6sXxp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180801205506kd8fCprbiYcJT57L.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180801205506dBIOphlLZGfXWwua.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180801205507LY3Qv9HzReirAmjU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667500\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.regular.company/stone-collection/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Regular Company</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Ergo Spout by Culinesco</h3><p>什么是梅森杯（Mason jar）？在没有冰箱的 1858 年，为了延长食物的保鲜期，美国铁匠 John L. Mason 发明了一种瓶子保存食物，玻璃瓶加密封胶圈。如今它已经成了网红罐子，尤其是在夏天，人们更是喜欢拿它来做各种甜品、冷饮或是酸奶，称得上是拍照利器。</p><p>最近，设计师 Jason Klug 推出了一款名为 Ergo Spout 的配件，希望让你的梅森杯更加好用。它可以将梅森杯转变为浇注式的水壶，用于柠檬水、鸡尾酒、调料等借口。</p><p>Ergo Spout 的设计适用于普通尺寸的梅森杯，设计有防滴漏口，橡胶垫圈，可实现紧密密封，保持物品新鲜。柔软的手柄和易于使用的翻盖，也拓展了梅森杯的用途。目前，它在众筹平台 Kickstarter 上的早鸟价格为 15 美元，<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/867812579/ergo-spout-ergonomic-spout-and-handle-for-mason-ja?utm_source=www.yankodesign.com&amp;utm_medium=kickbooster&amp;utm_content=link&amp;utm_campaign=af4e625f\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2018080120560441CFzUlrYpgoaJ7L.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180801205604Na7cXURpoZ9iL2m5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750476\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180801205605VW9GPQetoKzvMCAj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.928571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180801205605hHBKiwu316UR0nvM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.702857\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180801205606WIfdQqr1Z5jCk73u.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750476\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/867812579/ergo-spout-ergonomic-spout-and-handle-for-mason-ja?utm_source=www.yankodesign.com&amp;utm_medium=kickbooster&amp;utm_content=link&amp;utm_campaign=af4e625f\" rel=\"nofollow\">Kickstarter</a></figcaption></figure></div>"}